14:25.777 --> 14:27.083
Oh, fine.

14:27.127 --> 14:30.043
You cross-examine him,
because this is bullshit.

14:30.086 --> 14:31.435
This is motherfucking bullshit.

14:31.479 --> 14:33.916
You want to come after me,
you come after me

14:33.960 --> 14:37.615
