about my lack of competence,

14:37.659 --> 14:40.401
-my lack of worth.
-Your unworthiness--

14:40.444 --> 14:42.925
which you don't seem
to want to acknowledge--

14:42.969 --> 14:46.842
is you can't be the top dog
in a Black firm.

14:50.193 --> 14:52.239
Wake up.

14:57.679 --> 14:59.942
Ever shoot anybody?

14:59.986 --> 15:01.291
No, ma'am.

15:01.335 --> 15:02.989
Not in 11 years of service.

15:03.032 --> 15:05.905
Other than on the occasion
