26:03.605 --> 26:04.998
They just looked at me
like I compelled Joey

26:05.041 --> 26:06.347
to quick masturbate.

26:06.390 --> 26:08.741
My manager told me
to shut my mouth,

26:08.784 --> 26:10.438
-or it would ruin my career.
-And did it?

26:10.481 --> 26:13.310
The first gig I had
as a headliner got canceled.

26:14.268 --> 26:16.052
Things went south after that.

26:16.096 --> 26:18.141
Has your career ever rebounded?

26:18.185 --> 26:19.882
Fuck no. Hmm-mm.

26:19.926 --> 26:21.754
I'm sorry, June.

26:21.797 --> 26:24.104
Nothing further.

26:28.935 --> 26:30.458
Ms. Barrow,

26:30.501 --> 26:35.289
you had a headliner gig
canceled on July 11, 2019?

26:35.332 --> 26:37.639
-Is that right?
-Uh-huh.

26:37.683 --> 26:40.860
